| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3084 — Recovery Inhibition (meow)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f420bd3-6fcd-5d6e-8180-d9d40e6d4b01"
